  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The below wiki page explains the overview of getting the call stack for issue anlaysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Getting Complete Call stack - Aurix - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Getting instruction address which caused NMI trap - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Now this logic is implemented to log the call stack in case of WDG issues in Aurix China Convergence projects. Below wiki explains the log format"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SM06_Error Log Format - GEN4 generic - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Now this wiki page is to explain how to re-create the call stack from DLT log using Lauterbach and Trace 32."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Prerequisite"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "OUT binary - We need the out file of the binary in which the issue happens and log was stored"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Steps:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 1: Connect Trace32 to the target"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 2: Load the out file in which issue was reported by using the command"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Data.LOAD.elf xyz.out /NoCODE"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 3: Get the call stack information from DLT log as explained in SM06_Error Log Format - GEN4 generic - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "114623 2023/08/01 14:23:02.164233 0.0246 23 ECU1 SSH_ SEH_ 4132 log info verbose 1 Fusa_GID_1_SID_1#51132A08004A808013656A801B0CAE801B0D7C8014308C801DE4EEAE#"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The call stack information from above log is"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "8013656A 801B0CAE 801B0D7C 8014308C 801DE4EE"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 4: Get the call stack information using Dump window."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Open dump window - View → Dump",
        "Paste the address that we got from step 3"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Getting%20Call%20Stack%20from%20DLT%20log/image-2023-8-2_10-55-20.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Getting Call Stack from DLT log/image-2023-8-2_10-55-20.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Right click on the address and click on Display Memory → View"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Getting%20Call%20Stack%20from%20DLT%20log/image-2023-8-2_10-56-6.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Getting Call Stack from DLT log/image-2023-8-2_10-56-6.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "View window will show the instruction and function details"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Getting%20Call%20Stack%20from%20DLT%20log/image-2023-8-2_10-57-46.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Getting Call Stack from DLT log/image-2023-8-2_10-57-46.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Repeat the same steps for remaining addresses that we got from step 3, we can get complete call stack information"
      ]
    },
    {
